questions.problem: Starting in motion, an object speeds up to a given speed, in a given period of time. Find the magnitude of the object's acceleration if...
Beginning at rest, an object travels at a constant acceleration for a given period of time. Find the magnitude of the object's displacement if...
questions.formula: acceleration mul time mul time div 2

questions.problem: A book with a given mass sits still on the top of a desk. What is the magnitude of the normal force exerted on the book from the desk?
A pencil, not in motion, is suspended on a taut string. Determine the stretch (delta x) of the string if ...
questions.formula: sqrt ( ( ( Fy - ( mass mul g ) ) mul 2 ) div mass )
